## Family  

- **First marriage (1770)** to **Lady Charlotte Ponsonby**, daughter of **William Ponsonby, 2nd Earl of Bessborough**.  
- **Second marriage (1823)** to **Hon. Louisa Molesworth**, daughter of **Richard Molesworth, 3rd Viscount Molesworth**, and widow of **William Ponsonby, 1st Baron Ponsonby**.  

Children:  

- **Charles Wentworth‑Fitzwilliam, 5th Earl Fitzwilliam** [Charles_Wentworth‑Fitzwilliam,_5th_Earl_Fitzwilliam] (by his first wife).  

He died on 8 February 1833, aged 84, and was succeeded by his son from the first marriage.  

